✈️ AI Flight Agent

AI Flight Agent is a chat-based travel assistant built using OpenAI, Gradio, and Colab.
It helps users find flight details (airline, timings, prices) between cities and also generates AI-powered travel posters of destinations.

🚀 Features

💬 Chat-based interface with short, courteous responses.

✈️ Flight search from a mock flight database (airlines, timings, prices).

🎨 Travel poster generator using OpenAI’s DALL·E 3.

🖥️ Modern Gradio UI with dark theme.

⚙️ Tool calling support to connect chat and flight lookup logic.
